select b1.chapter_tag, b1.roll_number, b1.name,b1.worksheet_status,sd.school_name,sci.std,sm.section from(SELECT wt.chapter_tag , wt.roll_number,sd.name ,wt.section_id, case
						when wt.status = 1 then 'pdf generated'
							when wt.status = 2 then 'Printed'
							when wt.status = 3 then 'Delivered'
							when wt.status = 4 then 'Reprint Requested'
							else null
						end as worksheet_status 
FROM worksheet.worksheet_track wt
join  app.master_student_data sd
on wt.roll_number = sd.roll_number
where status =1)b1
join public.section_master sm on 
		b1.section_id = sm.section_id
join public.school_class_info sci on
		sm.class_id = sci.class_id
join public.lb_school_details sd on
		sci.school_id = sd.school_id
 
 order by b1.roll_number
